{
    "name": "Xaxmellia",
    "type": "alien",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Xaxmellias are kaiju native to Daimalko. The first rose from an acidic lake in the caldera of a quiescent volcano, and the volcano erupted soon after. These colossi are capable of burrowing through soil and rubble in a bizarre corkscrew fashion, using this ability to hide and then ambushing prey, including rival kaiju.<br/><br/>The typical xaxmellia is 70 feet tall."
        }
    ],
